text: Cosmotomidius egregius is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Martins and Galileo in 2007. It is known from Bolivia.BioLib.cz - Cosmotomidius egregius. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Pogonocherini Category:Beetles described in 2007
title: Cosmotomidius egregius
